{"tid":1558052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聽日9點半去聲援畫家！！7月一直還押到宜家！告成9條罪啊！！","createTime":"2019-09-10T10:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T23:07:23.000Z","uid":273492,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"0a50318f3ac182dd1002c7c30c7807bd9446d962","tid":1558052,"uid":273492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190705/large/1562296984_03a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190705%2Flarge%2F1562296984_03a3.jpg&h=77a17eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫家上一次帶淚抵庭，投訴遭警撥下體疑似公安恐嚇送返大陸<br />\n<br />\n被捕人仕關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4QEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=2683e630\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\n［1］<br />\n日期：9月11日 9:30 am<br />\n地址：東區裁判法院 第7庭4樓<br />\n裁判官：黃士翔<br />\n被告：潘X超（畫家）<br />\n控罪：非法集結、7項襲警、刑事損壞<br />\n事件：621 包圍警總<br />\n備注：「畫家」被指在現場投擲雞蛋，蛋液濺中警總外牆、扶手電梯、七名警員(譚柔慧、文振寰、方志洋、盧偉東、陳梓軒、盧焯基、梁綽熙)及盾牌。控罪一變七，控方申請加控六罪，將七名警員疑受襲的案件分成七罪檢控帶淚抵庭；遭警撥下體；疑似公安恐嚇送返大陸<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有另一位手足申請保釋條件，本來要去波蘭做交換生</span></span><br />\n［2］<br />\n日期：9月11日 10:30 am<br />\n地址：高等法院 內庭聆訊(公開) 第33庭 13樓<br />\n法官：邱智立<br />\n被告：李X瑩<br />\n控罪：暴動11/11提堂（11/9申請更改保釋條件）<br />\n事件：829 深水埗<br />\n備注：曾留院，被捕受傷。禁離港赴波蘭作交換生，向高院申請更改保釋條件。"},{"pid":"e1b26036348969d159089f3fb419032f68af1bea","tid":1558052,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0650249d5a6b95cbd52c862b020e6dd1f8cdeee8","tid":1558052,"uid":450